%F A217922 T(n, k) = (n-1)*T(n-1, k) + (n+k-3)*T(n-1, k-1), for 1 <= k <= n-2, with T(n, 0) = (n-1)!. - _G. C. Greubel_, Jan 10 2025
%e A217922 Triangle begins:
%e A217922   \ k  0....1....2....3....4......
%e A217922   n
%e A217922   1 |..1
%e A217922   2 |..1
